<section xml:id="graphics_vocabulary">
<title>Vocabulary</title>
<ul>
<li>
<title>AWT:</title>
<p>
<idx><h>AWT</h></idx>
The <q>Abstract Window Toolkit</q>, a Java package for creating graphical user interfaces.</p></li>
<li>
<title>coordinate:</title>
<p>
<idx><h>coordinate</h></idx>
A value that specifies a location in a 2D graphical window.</p></li>
<li>
<title>pixel:</title>
<p>
<idx><h>pixel</h></idx>
The unit in which coordinates are measured.</p></li>
<li>
<title>bounding box:</title>
<p>
<idx><h>bounding box</h></idx>
A way to specify the coordinates of a rectangular area.</p></li>
<li>
<title>RGB:</title>
<p>
<idx><h>RGB</h></idx>
A color model based on adding red, green, and blue light.</p></li>
</ul>
</section>
